  "body": "I noticed in `/lodestar/packages/lodestar-params/src/interface.ts` that we have an object called ALL_FORKS, but this object is not in the mainnet or minimal configs (e.g. https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/configs/mainnet/phase0.yaml)\r\n\r\nMaybe we should remove ALL_FORKS so the interface and beacon chain params can be consistent and up-to-date with the spec/config?  Or move it somewhere else, if it's something we definitely need?  \r\n\r\nThoughts?\r\n\r\nRelated PR (where ALL_FORKS was created):\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/843",
